relation: I can't _possibly_ be the first one to come up with this joke.
Kudos to anyone who knows the reference.
We've all been there, at least either on the giving or the receiving end.
textBeforeTable: > W T S Q P N M I G F D C B A < Other Submissions by kenisu3000 Looking over my original of this page from two/three years ago, I noticed something I had forgotten about. A faint erasure can be seen in the sky, in the panel where Marilyn is on the ground (you probably can't see it here, since this is photocopy, and a colored one at that). It's a speech balloon of Marilyn going "AcK... gAHhh..." and it's accompanied by the sound effect "twitch twitch". All I can say is: *wow*, I'm really glad I recognized the mood killer there when I did. Camel's back = BROKEN. kenisu - #81 This image has been resized for your convenience. Click on it to view the full size version.
